                <div class="content_box">
                    <strong class="v_tit"><a href="/Cases/CasesDownLoad/1/1074" target="_blank">查看全文</a>&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;&nbsp;<a href="/Cases/Search">案例查询</a></strong>

                    <table cellspacing="2" cellpadding="0" style="margin:auto; width:750px;" class="infotable">

                        <tbody>
                            <tr><td colspan="2" height="30px" style="font-weight:bold; font-size:14px; background-color:#CCCCCC; padding-left:10px;">显示案例信息</td></tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例编号：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">FAM-0149</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">被浏览次数：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">9012 次</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">公司上市都是包装出来的吗？——惠鑫公司的IPO之路</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译名：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">Listed Companies Equal the Result of Packaging? ——IPO of Huixin Company</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例作者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">段宏</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">作者单位：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">西南交通大学</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">指导者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">译者：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;"></td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例企业名称：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">惠鑫机电设备制造股份有限公司</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">行业：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">机械、电机工业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">规模：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">大型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及的职能领域：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">财务管理部门</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例语种：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例正文页数（页）：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">22 页</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例类型：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">描述型</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">IPO；包装；民营企业</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文关键词：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">IPO; Packaging; Private Enterprise</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">中文摘要：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本案例描述了惠鑫机电设备制造股份有限公司从一个注册资本只有50万的民营小型企业起步，经历过增资扩股，股权结构调整，公司改制一系列的运作，2008年成长为一个注册资本4000万的股份有限公司，经过三年的辅导期，规范了出资、财务等一系列问题，于2010年5月成功上市的全过程。一直以来，如何能顺利的通过IPO之路，提升公司品质，扩大资本实力是很多公司关心并向往的。人们对公司的IPO过程甚感兴趣，但多数人只知其一，不解其二，加上近年来出现的上市公司丑闻使得大多数人一提及公司上市的财务处理就联想成财务包装，甚至财务舞弊。案例在客观描述公司基本情况的基础上，进一步分析了公司上市动机以及上市过程的整改细节，通过案例可以了解并学习规范的公司应该如何运作，不规范的公司应该如何规范，对很多希望上市的公司和相关从业人员有一定的借鉴意义。</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">英文摘要： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;word-break:keep-all">The case in the present paper describes how Huixin Mechanical and Electrical Engineering Limited Liability Company developed into a limited liability company with the registered capital of 40 million in 2008 from a private enterprise with the registered capital of 500 thousand through the increase of capital, the expansion of shares, the structural adjustment of shares and a serious of operations and how the company came into the company in May, 2010 after a counseling period of three years during which the company was standard in a serious of issues such as capital contribution and finance. For a long time, how to achieve IPO successfully, to develop the quality of the company and to expand capital is what many companies care about and yearn for. People have been interested in IPO, but most of them know little about it. Besides, the scandal of recent listed companies gives people the association of the financial dealing of listed companies with financial packaging or even financial cheating. Based on the objective description of the basic situation of the company, the present paper further analyzes the motives and the motives of coming into the market, and the adjustment details. The paper analyzes the advantages and disadvantages of private enterprise coming into the market. The paper also gives reflections about the financing and managing structure of private enterprise. </td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用对象： </th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">本科生,硕士生,工商管理硕士（MBA）,</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">编写方式：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">采编/一手资料编写</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例年代：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2010</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">适用课程：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">《会计学》、《财务管理》</td>
                            </tr>
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例涉及理论知识：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">IPO上市</td>
                            </tr>
                            
                            
                            <tr>
                                <th style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">案例入库时间：</th>
                                <td style="background-color:#EBEBEB;">2012-12</td>
                            </tr>
